Privacy Policy
----------------

### Introduction

Welcome to Addition Salon Agra's Privacy Policy. This policy outlines the information we collect, how we use it, and the choices you have regarding your personal information.

Harsh Verma is the developer of the Addition Salon Agra app, which is provided free of charge by Addition Salon Agra. The app is designed to showcase salon services along with their respective prices. It does not involve any costs or payment methods.

By using our Service, you agree to the collection and use of information as described in this policy. The Personal Information we collect is used to enhance and provide the Service. We will not use or disclose your information to anyone except as described in this Privacy Policy.

The terms used in this Privacy Policy have the same meanings as in our Terms and Conditions, accessible on our website, unless otherwise defined in this Privacy Policy.

### Information Collection and Use

To offer you the best possible experience while using our Service, we may request and retain certain information, including but not limited to the user's name. The information collected will be used as described in this privacy policy.

The app does not utilize third-party services that may gather information for the purpose of identifying you.

### Security

We highly value your trust in providing us with your Personal Information. Therefore, we are committed to using commercially acceptable methods to protect it. However, please be aware that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure and reliable, and we cannot guarantee its absolute security.

